{"type":"article","id":17367,"title":"有点儿想退坑碧蓝航线","uid":15353,"topics":[6674,3138,6278,81],"contents":"官方对舰娘事件的处理手法曾经被赞过，很多人都说它公关做得好，但自从“港独角兽”事件后，大家就知道官方的公关在处理政治风波的方面原来就是一坨粪。 四月四日停服一整天（之前还说不要联系政治）竟然要关台服，官方给的补偿竟然比平常维护（几个小时）给的还少，限时兑换没延长，脸书专面上一片骂声官方还装死。现在官方脸书被中国武汉肺炎洗版了，谷歌商店的评分掉至1.3历史新低，隔壁少前崩3rd也没搞成这样。<br>\n<br>\n重点：我在聊天室说了敏感词被共狗检举，禁言两天，这个让我萌生了退坑念头<br>\n<br>\n该退坑吗？<a href=\"https://i.imgur.com/RqVrkUr.png\" rel=\"nofollow noreferrer noopener\" target=\"_blank\"><img src=\"https://i.imgur.com/RqVrkUr.png\" alt=\"https://i.imgur.com/RqVrkUr.png\" style=\"max-width:100%\"></a><a href=\"https://i.imgur.com/5rcW2qC.png\" rel=\"nofollow noreferrer noopener\" target=\"_blank\"><img src=\"https://i.imgur.com/5rcW2qC.png\" alt=\"https://i.imgur.com/5rcW2qC.png\" style=\"max-width:100%\"></a><a href=\"https://i.imgur.com/aQjAiG5.png\" rel=\"nofollow noreferrer noopener\" target=\"_blank\"><img src=\"https://i.imgur.com/aQjAiG5.png\" alt=\"https://i.imgur.com/aQjAiG5.png\" style=\"max-width:100%\"></a><a href=\"https://i.imgur.com/fYyTfHN.png\" rel=\"nofollow noreferrer noopener\" target=\"_blank\"><img src=\"https://i.imgur.com/fYyTfHN.png\" alt=\"https://i.imgur.com/fYyTfHN.png\" style=\"max-width:100%\"></a>","date":"2020-04-06","agreeCount":13,"discussionCount":0}